parts.text: Despite years of training, she still felt like an amateur in the metier of international diplomacy.
The bard strummed a mournful melody on his ancient lyre, its strings echoing the sorrow of the fallen king.
The artist assiduously worked on her masterpiece, meticulously blending colors and shaping details for hours on end.
Despite the storm raging outside, her **mien** remained calm and collected, inspiring confidence in those around her.
The lack of funding completely stymied the research team's progress on the groundbreaking project.
The neophyte nervously navigated the complex controls of the spaceship, relying heavily on the experienced pilot's guidance.
The professor's extensive research was compiled into a series of scholarly treatises on the history of ancient civilizations.
